ted to resolve with a regular adblock rule because the website is being protected by service of Ad-Shield that is an anti-adblock company.\n\n## Userscript Installation\nPlease block Ad-Shield advertisement by installing [tinyShield userscript](https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield).\nPlease check its installation guideline written in English by visiting [this URL](https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield/blob/main/README.md).\n\nIf you can understand Korean language, please refer https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield/blob/main/README.ko.md.\n\nNew change of tinyShield's build script for Apple Safari Extension user (made at 2026 Apr 21) is available.\n\n## Still Have a Problem?\nAn issue is occurred when the userscript is applied, please report to [this issue tracker](https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield/issues).","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/222607/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/222607/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"pinned_comment":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/comments/4348403461","html_url":"https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/222607#issuecomment-4348403461","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/222607","id":4348403461,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAVlsM88AAAABAy9fBQ","user":{"login":"aerial3701","id":274669899,"node_id":"U_kgDOEF8hSw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/274669899?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/aerial3701","html_url":"https://github.com/aerial3701","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aerial3701/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aerial3701/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aerial3701/gist